tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE contestant_profiles (
  contestant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(50),
  age INT,
  location VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE contestant_profiles (
    contestant_id INT,
    contestant_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    hometown VARCHAR(50),
    PRIMARY KEY (contestant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE competition_outcomes (
    outcome_id INT,
    contestant_id INT,
    competition_date DATE,
    rank INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (outcome_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (contestant_id) REFERENCES contestant_profiles(contestant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Contestants (
    contestant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    contestant_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    hometown VARCHAR(50),
    specialty_cuisine VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE JudgeFeedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    competition_id INT,
    contestant_id INT,
    judge_name VARCHAR(50),
    feedback_text TEXT,
    score INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (competition_id) REFERENCES Competitions(competition_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (contestant_id) REFERENCES Contestants(contestant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Winners (
    winner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    competition_id INT,
    contestant_id INT,
    prize VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (competition_id) REFERENCES Competitions(competition_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (contestant_id) REFERENCES Contestants(contestant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Auditions (
    audition_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    contestant_id INT,
    audition_date DATE,
    passed BOOLEAN,
    FOREIGN KEY (contestant_id) REFERENCES Contestants(contestant_id)
);
